    dc:description "Text-fig. 6. Scatter diagrams (length and width) of Typhlomys aff. T. primitivus measurements from Leilao, Yuanmou in comparison with those of T. hipparionum and T. storchi from Leilao, and of T. primitivus and T. hipparionum from Shihuiba, Lufeng." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5382375/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

